The social card of a resident of the Ivanovo region is recognized as an electronic means of payment.
The changes provide for the preservation of benefits for travel in public passenger transport.
Since September 24, the procedure for organizing preferential travel of citizens using a social card of a resident of the Ivanovo region has changed.
According to the press service of the Russian government in the Ivanovo region, the changes provide for the preservation of the benefits for travel in public passenger transport and give a scheme of mutual settlements on the social card in line with the requirements of Federal Law No. 161 of the Federal Law "On the National Payment System".
At the same time, the social card of a resident of the Ivanovo region is recognized as an electronic means of payment.
Accordingly, the conditions for its application change.
So, the replenishment limit is now set not in trips, as before, but in the amount of money, with the preservation of winter and summer periods - in winter - in winter no more than 400 rubles, in the summer - no more than 800 rubles for the current month.
Now the owners of the social card on the receipts issued in transport will need to track not the number of remaining trips, but the balance of funds.
The cost of preferential travel for citizens will be 1/2 of the tariff in force for the carrier.
The remaining half of the cost of travel reimburses the regional budget.
The schedule of replenishment of the social card by funds remains the same - in the period from 24 of the previous month to the 23rd day of the current month.
The new procedure for travel on the social map will have a number of advantages.
So, it becomes possible to keep a detailed record of spending money on a social card with an accuracy of kopecks.
In addition, it is possible to return the credited, but unspent funds.
We also add that the scheme of mutual settlements with carriers becomes transparent, since now half the cost of travel is paid by a citizen, and exactly the same amount reimburses the carrier for the budget.
No commission will be charged when making money on the card.
In turn, Vasily Silkin, deputy head of the Department of Roads and Transport of the Ivanovo region, said that in 2014 more than 33 million trips were made in the region using a social card, in 2015 - almost 25 million trips.
In the regional budget for the provision of preferential travel of citizens using the social card, more than 470 million rubles are provided.
As of September 1, the amount of compensation for these purposes amounted to more than 312 million rubles.
