Russian human rights activist, LGBT activist (LGBT - lesbians, gay, bisexual, transgender) Nikolai Alekseev supported the idea of creating special places to serve the punishment for transgender, noting that abroad it is also possible to determine people in the colony - male or female - depending on their own desire.
