At the end of the meeting, the chairman with high-profile accusations was attacked by a member of the Communist Party Sergei Samokhin, shouting that the election commission ignores dozens of complaints and covers falsifications in the elections.
"You're not here at a rally, be careful to say!" - offended the chairman of the election commission.
As a result, the protocol was approved almost unanimously.
